- Thank you.

00:36:57.980 --> 00:36:59.750
Really enjoyed the talk.

00:36:59.750 --> 00:37:00.890
I had a question.

00:37:00.890 --> 00:37:05.280
You said that detecting
a signal would suggest

00:37:05.280 --> 00:37:08.570
