00:38:44.470 --> 00:38:49.080
But in media, in
certain television

00:38:49.080 --> 00:38:54.480
series like The X-Files,
in movies, a lot of them

00:38:54.480 --> 00:39:02.280
perpetuate this idea that if
contact had been made already,

00:39:02.280 --> 00:39:05.180
our government would
hide it from us.

00:39:05.180 --> 00:39:12.190
And I was just curious
about hearing from you,

00:39:12.190 --> 00:39:14.640
one of the people that
would be the first to know--

00:39:14.640 --> 00:39:17.436
