00:44:28.440 --> 00:44:36.430
for recognizing any
sort of alien signal?

00:44:36.430 --> 00:44:40.060
- Well, so there a lot of
bright lights up there.

00:44:40.060 --> 00:44:42.550
And I can put my thumb
